  <p>Disclaimer: I know that the buzzword is used to define <em>roles</em> instead of a culture change, with the objective to join <code class="highlighter-rouge">dev</code> and <code class="highlighter-rouge">ops</code> teams, but you know that this doesnâ€™t happen in most cases, so why not.</p>
